== Japanese ==
===Stroke Order===
[[Image:Japanese Hiragana E.png]]

===Etymology===
Simplified in the [[w:Heian period|Heian period]] from the ''[[man'yōgana]]'' ([[万葉仮名]]) kanji [[衣]] (''e'')

===Hiragana character===
'''え''' (''e'')

# the [e] phoneme, typically in words of Japanese origin
#: The fourth character of first column of the [[hiragana]] [[syllabary]], it is analogous to [[エ]] (''e'') in the [[katakana]] syllabary. The previous hiragana character is [[う]] (''u'') and the next is [[お]] (''o'').

====Related terms====
* For a list of words starting with え (''e'') see: [[Wiktionary:Japanese index え]]

===Noun=== 
'''え''' (''e'')
# [[餌]]: [[bait]], [[lure]]
# [[柄]]: [[handle]], [[shaft]], [[gripe]], [[helve]]
# [[絵]], [[画]]: [[picture]], [[painting]], [[drawing]], [[illustration]], [[tableau]]

